<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
  <title>Subprocessors — SourcemAI</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/theme.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/app.css">
</head>
<body class="legal-page">
  <header class="legal-header"><a href="/" class="brand">SourcemAI</a></header>
  <main class="legal-main">
    <h1>Subprocessors</h1>
    <p class="muted">Last updated: <%= lastUpdated %></p>
    <p>SourcemAI uses the following subprocessors to deliver the service. Customers are notified 30 days before any change.</p>
    <table class="data-table">
      <thead><tr><th>Subprocessor</th><th>Purpose</th><th>Region</th></tr></thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td>Render</td><td>Application hosting</td><td>US (Oregon)</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Neon</td><td>Postgres hosting</td><td>US (AWS)</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Cloudflare R2</td><td>Image asset delivery</td><td>Global</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Polsia Email Proxy</td><td>Transactional email delivery</td><td>US</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Stripe</td><td>Payments</td><td>US</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Sentry</td><td>Error tracking</td><td>US</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Polsia AI</td><td>Prospect research, email generation, reply categorization</td><td>US</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Crunchbase</td><td>Funding signal source</td><td>US</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
    <p>Salesforce, HubSpot, Greenhouse, Lever, Gmail, Microsoft 365, and Zapier are integrated on a per-customer basis only when explicitly connected.</p>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
